# 🧪 Generic Test Case Document  

This repository contains **sample manual test cases** that can be applied across different domains (e-commerce, travel, banking, healthcare, etc.).  
Each test case is designed with **traceability, clarity, and reusability** in mind.  

---

## 📑 Test Case Format  

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Test Case ID** | Unique identifier (e.g., TC_Login_001) |
| **Module** | Application module under test |
| **Title / Scenario** | Short description of what is being tested |
| **Preconditions** | Setup required before executing the test |
| **Test Steps** | Step-by-step actions to perform |
| **Expected Result** | The outcome if the application works correctly |
| **Actual Result** | The outcome observed during execution |
| **Status** | Pass / Fail / Blocked / Not Executed |
| **Defect Reference** | Link/ID of bug in JIRA, TestRail, etc. |

---

## ✅ Sample Test Cases  

### 🔐 Login Module  

| Test Case ID | Module | Title | Preconditions | Test Steps | Expected Result | Status | Defect Reference |
|--------------|--------|-------|---------------|------------|-----------------|--------|------------------|
| TC_Login_001 | Login | Verify login with valid credentials | User must be registered | 1. Navigate to login page <br> 2. Enter valid username & password <br> 3. Click **Login** | User is redirected to dashboard | Pass | N/A |
| TC_Login_002 | Login | Verify login with invalid password | User must be registered | 1. Navigate to login page <br> 2. Enter valid username & invalid password <br> 3. Click **Login** | System shows error: *Invalid username or password* | Pass | N/A |

---

### 📝 Registration Module  

| Test Case ID | Module | Title | Preconditions | Test Steps | Expected Result | Status | Defect Reference |
|--------------|--------|-------|---------------|------------|-----------------|--------|------------------|
| TC_Reg_001 | Registration | Verify new user registration | User not registered | 1. Open Registration page <br> 2. Fill mandatory fields (Name, Email, Password) <br> 3. Submit form | Account created & confirmation email sent | Pass | N/A |
| TC_Reg_002 | Registration | Verify registration with existing email | Email already registered | 1. Open Registration page <br> 2. Enter already registered email <br> 3. Submit form | Error: *Email already exists* | Fail | BUG-101 |

---

### 🔎 Search Module  

| Test Case ID | Module | Title | Preconditions | Test Steps | Expected Result | Status | Defect Reference |
|--------------|--------|-------|---------------|------------|-----------------|--------|------------------|
| TC_Search_001 | Search | Verify search with valid keyword | User logged in | 1. Enter valid keyword in search bar <br> 2. Click **Search** | Relevant search results displayed | Pass | N/A |
| TC_Search_002 | Search | Verify search with invalid keyword | User logged in | 1. Enter random text `xyz@@` <br> 2. Click **Search** | No results found message should display | Pass | N/A |

---

### 💳 Payment Module  

| Test Case ID | Module | Title | Preconditions | Test Steps | Expected Result | Status | Defect Reference |
|--------------|--------|-------|---------------|------------|-----------------|--------|------------------|
| TC_Pay_001 | Payment | Verify payment with valid credit card | User logged in & product in cart | 1. Proceed to checkout <br> 2. Select **Credit Card** <br> 3. Enter valid details <br> 4. Submit payment | Payment successful & order confirmed | Pass | N/A |
| TC_Pay_002 | Payment | Verify payment with expired credit card | User logged in & product in cart | 1. Proceed to checkout <br> 2. Select **Credit Card** <br> 3. Enter expired card details <br> 4. Submit payment | Error: *Card expired / Invalid* | Fail | BUG-102 |

