| Test Case ID | Module | Title | Preconditions | Test Steps | Expected Result | Status | Defect Reference |
|--------------|--------|-------|---------------|------------|-----------------|--------|------------------|
| TC_Logout_001 | Logout | Verify successful logout | User must be logged in | 1. Click **Logout** button | User logged out & redirected to homepage | Pass | N/A |

---

## 📊 Execution Status Legend  

- **Pass** ✅ – Test executed successfully, meets expected result  
- **Fail** ❌ – Test executed but outcome not as expected  
- **Blocked** ⛔ – Test cannot be executed due to dependencies  
- **Not Executed** ⏳ – Test not yet run  

---

## 🛠 Tools for Test Case Management  

- **TestRail** – Test case management & reporting  
- **TestLink** – Open-source test case management  
- **JIRA / ClickUp / Redmine** – Defect tracking & linking test cases  

---

📌 This structure can be **directly reused for GitHub repos** or shared with teams for **manual testing documentation**.  
